text: Liang Hongyu (; born 23 October 1990) is a Chinese professional racing cyclist, who last rode for UCI Women's Team . She is from Heilongjiang. ==See also== * List of 2015 UCI Women's Teams and riders ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese female cyclists Category:Cyclists from Heilongjiang Category:Cyclists at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games competitors for China
